 200 美元。</p><p> S95B 的 QD-OLED 面板将 OLED 技术与量子点层相结合，使其能够提供高对比度和宽视角，而不会在亮度和色彩饱和度方面牺牲典型 OLED 电视的性能。这意味着即使在更明亮的房间里它也应该提供丰富的图像。它还可以播放高达 4K 120Hz 的内容，这对于 PS5 或 Xbox Series X 来说很方便，但与所有三星电视一样，它不支持杜比视界 HDR。</p><p> S95B 是 2022 年的型号，因此它即将淘汰，取而代之的是<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJXRlNGRDdQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTEzNi0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdwL8-cCoYISluuCpJO0vG6PonGZoxkCPy14Ny1jajz7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFSFD7P" class="rapid-with-clickid">新的 S95C</a> 。后者支持更快的 144Hz 刷新率，并通过外部盒子运行其端口，这使得设计更薄。其他<a data-i13n="cpos:51;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/reviews/samsung/s95c-oled">评论家</a><a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/features/samsung-s95b-vs-samsung-s95c-which-should-you-buy">说它</a>也可以变得更亮一点。但目前 S95 55 英寸和 65 英寸型号的售价分别为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:53;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJXRlNGRDdQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTEzNi0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYWFkZDA1OTYtMTYwYi00ZWUyLWIyMDQtODEzNmFhYjljZTYzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdwL8-cCoYISluuCpJO0vG6PonGZoxkCPy14Ny1jajz7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFSFD7P" class="rapid-with-clickid">2,298 美元</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affi