ime Day 优惠。</p><h2> AirPods Pro（第二代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="ba359120b39d4bf9b1b9b5e3379f1bea" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAThTWLFJ1_6jDdor75Ndek1uPvqfNtiiMIjGKCtZIMvq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0BDHWDR12" class="rapid-with-clickid">第二代 AirPods Pro</a>在 Prime Day 期间以 199 美元的价格出售。这是 50 美元的折扣，也是我们见过的最优惠的价格。在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">我们的耳塞指南</a>中，它们是 iPhone 用户的首选，与第一次迭代相比有了很大的改进，具有更好的降噪效果和整体改进的声音。它们具有出色的透明模式，让您在听音乐的同时仍能留意周围的声音，它们与 iPhone、iPad 和 Mac 完美搭配，并充分利用 Siri 的帮助。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html">我们</a><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html">在评测中给了他们 88 分</a>，指出音质既身临其境又细致，即使在较低音量下也能保持清晰。电池续航时间比苹果承诺的 6 小时多了 15 分钟，而且充电盒还能为耳机多充电 3 次。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html"><strong>阅读我们对 Apple AirPods Pro（第二代）的完整评论</strong></a></p><h2>AirPods（第 3 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="ebb499ea37c04874b033149e33cf6527" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple 更新版<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQuzFNN_zyKG0dueAZsGRNMrT_TyPXS7BXapegtBL-R2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Lightning-Resist