com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">对于大多数人来说这是最好的 iPad</a> 。它于 2022 年推出，配备苹果自己的 M1 片上系统处理器和明亮锐利的 10.9 英寸显示屏。我们给它的<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-air-5th-generation-review-130019050.html">评分为 90 分</a>，指出更新的芯片和 5G 功能（在<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlWM0pCMk5EP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAbXyOzerJfnXbE0BN_FlMKFIK_xDbkK3AU-8slqk4Obp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09V3JB2ND" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09V3JB2ND?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">蜂窝模型</a>上）使其“几乎面向未来”。</p><p>它非常适合玩游戏和观看节目，但当你将它与键盘等配件配对时，iPad Air 可以轻松处理生产力任务，例如写作、绘图、适度的照片编辑以及运行 Airtable 和 Slack 等与工作相关的应用程序。而且它比<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATULpOmXhNo4B8X-gW0KfYhyu6I1UiWEmeBz0A4DWPcy&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-12-9-inch-iPad-Pro-Wi-Fi-128GB%2Fdp%2FB0BJLF2BRM" class="rapid-with-clickid">iPad Pro</a>便宜得多，这对许多用户来说可能有点大材小用。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-air-5th-generation-review-130019050.html"><strong>阅读我们对 iPad Air 的完整评论。</strong></a></p><h2> iPad（第 9 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="843dbab7ad4e46dab244e0e6f6562c6c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;se