页按钮，这很好，但取消了耳机插孔，这不太好。</p><h2> MacBook Air M1 </h2><p><core-commerce id="234f60531f574d228c10e486d83bf01b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果您想以便宜的价格购买 Apple 笔记本电脑，请选择<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARoBT_99zjj_Wcz5lmIA7pDrBDIN9-uqbtRzEQ8iokp9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MacBook-13-inch-256GB-Storage%2Fdp%2FB08N5LNQCX" class="rapid-with-clickid">配备 M1 芯片的 2020 款 MacBook Air</a> 。它仍然是一款功能强大的笔记本电脑，256GB 基本型号在 Prime Day 仅需 750 美元，这是迄今为止我们在超便携笔记本上看到的最低价格。它是我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-macbook-140032524.html">Macbook 购买者指南</a>中的预算之选，并在我们的评测中获得了<a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-macbook-air-m1-review-140031323.html">94 分的高分</a>。</p><p> M1 芯片的性能确实让 MacBook Air M1 脱颖而出。它反应灵敏，可以快速启动应用程序并轻松运行它们。 M1 芯片也是 MB Air 出色电池续航时间的重要原因。我们在视频总结测试中获得了 16 小时 20 分钟的播放时间，这应该足以让您完成一整天的工作或学习。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-macbook-air-m1-review-140031323.html"><strong>请阅读我们对配备 M1 芯片的 MacBook Air 的（相当热情的）评论。</strong></a></p><h2>小型平板电脑</h2><p><core-commerce id="9deb0115288047edac25b52a7800b2ad" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>像<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlHOTFMWEZQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdmjsmdQm75aE4mQZ8cNXuA-vNzZuxWpyX1iB4rkt8Gy&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G91LXFP" class="rapid-with-clickid">iPad mini</a>这样的小型平板电脑可以完成手机的许多功能，同时为您提供更多的屏幕空间。在 Prime Day 当天，苹果为 Prime 会员提供的小额优惠为 380 美元，而不是通常的 499 美元。由于其新颖的设计和稳定的性能，我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-mini-6th-generation-2021-review-130009170.html">评测</a>中给了 mini 89 分。它还与第二代<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXytOIsQTlSMWEu0r7dlhAGSrfNYne9qXWOs9Ks1tgAm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation%2Fdp%2FB07K1WWBJK" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Pencil</a>完美搭配，将 mini 变成便携式数字笔记本。</p><p> iPad mini 配备 12MP 超宽前置摄像头，支持 ​​Center Stage，该功能可平移和缩放，让您在视频通话期间保持在画面中。至于电池续航时间，苹果估计一次充电可以使用 10 小时，但我们的视频运行测试比我们的视频续航时间长了两个小时，而且在休闲但经常使用的情况下，只需每隔一天充电一次。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-mini-6th-generation-2021-review-130009170.html"><strong>阅读我们对 iPad Mini 的完整评论</strong></a></p><h2>Apple Pencil（第二代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="a7ac3b8968534a1c92a72870c4a3db68" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>最新款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXytOIsQTlSMWEu0r7dlhAGSrfNYne9qXWOs9Ks1tgAm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation%2Fdp%2FB07K1WWBJK" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Pencil</a>通常售价 129 美元，但 Prime Day 仅需 89 美元。第二代手写笔<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&