13n="cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://www.steamdeck.com/en/tech">这</a>两个<a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1" href="https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/22481/~/microsd-card-faq">系统</a>都仅限于官方<a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://www.sdcard.org/developers/sd-standard-overview/bus-speed-default-speed-high-speed-uhs-sd-express/">UHS-I 总线速度</a>，因此只要您的卡满足特定阈值（Evo Select 就是如此），所有 microSD 卡的游戏启动和加载时间几乎相同。您主要想要的是花很少的钱获得大量的存储空间。在这个价位上，Evo Select 可以满足您的需求。</p><p>如果您需要更多空间， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEI3TllOM04zP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFjOC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTI0ZTlmOTktYWVkOC00ZDQwLWJjMjAtMjRhYmE3ZjJlZjE3In0&amp;signature=AQAAAdeCbSVmS6tnmIiaYutqM0HLq_2NYg9Uo2HDK9G6tK_p&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B7NYN3N3" class="rapid-with-clickid">1TB SanDisk Ultra</a>也值得一试，售价为 80 美元，这是历史最低价。这张卡比 Evo Select 慢，Evo Select 已经是预算型号，所以为了舒适而安装游戏可能有点太慢了。但 80 美元 1TB 确实物超所值。</p><p>我们的 microSD 卡指南中的首选是<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEMxUEdWNzU2P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFjOC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTI0ZTlmOTktYWVkOC00ZDQwLWJjMjAtMjRhYmE3ZjJlZjE3In0&amp;signature=AQAAAT2wKfJ0edfcBRa9cPAm2lX4OLRekDWreYa5hZyRS0W_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C1PG