适，麦克风很好，而且电池对于最大限度地减少无线耳机常见的不便大有帮助。请注意，耳机仅通过 USB 无线适配器连接，不能与 Xbox 配合使用。</p><h2> HyperX 云毒刺 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="03ae81715ad34587ab317a97626feda7" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEI4UEdETVdLP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFjOC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTI0ZTlmOTktYWVkOC00ZDQwLWJjMjAtMjRhYmE3ZjJlZjE3In0&amp;signature=AQAAAZ3uavQzRQfYZv8lMze4YjnVUtYnWIw-M_sdqi2b0JFH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B8PGDMWK" class="rapid-with-clickid">HyperX Cloud Stinger 2</a>也以 35 美元的新低价格发售。这是我们购买指南中的预算选择。它的声音不是特别平衡，但它给动作场景带来了令人兴奋的冲击感，而且它的麦克风质量掩盖了低廉的价格。塑料框架也不会太紧，但感觉确实有点廉价。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJIVjJKVDgxP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFjOC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTI0ZTlmOTktYWVkOC00ZDQwLWJjMjAtMjRhYmE3ZjJlZjE3In0&amp;signature=AQAAAf_CZbhJM9yBJ1qUTFgKb8mJsGYq5YRVYb1wu2UlGSYr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BHV2JT81" class="rapid-with-clickid">最初的 Cloud Stinger</a>也以 20 美元的价格出售，虽然新型号听起来更好，但这个价格很优惠。</p><h2>罗技 G535 </h2><p><core-commerce id="a05bc734b28347dba1fcb36bfe7882ff" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:51;pos:1" href="https://shopping.