tle><![CDATA[The best Amazon Prime Day headphone deals for 2023]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tesla reportedly suspected Musk was using company funds to build a literal glass house]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>特斯拉可能已经对首席执行官埃隆·马斯克可能存在的不当行为进行了调查。 <em>《华尔街日报》</em>的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfmy2fUr9R1uPoz_d9Z_JwlNSDJo8kaBXGrdSclLXhML&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fa-glass-house-for-elon-musk-sparks-internal-tesla-probe-9a121db5%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos5" class="rapid-with-clickid">消息人士</a>称，这家电动汽车制造商的董事会因担心马斯克可能使用公司资金在奥斯汀地区超级工厂附近建造房屋而展开调查。该计划被昵称为“Project 42”，据信涉及购买价值数百万美元的特种玻璃——金额大到去年引起了员工的关注。据了解，与马斯克及其高管有关联的有限责任公司也在该地区购买了大量土地。</p><p>这座房子的概念包括“扭曲的六边形”或玻璃立方体，让人想起苹果第五大道商店。消息人士称，这似乎是个人空间，因为它包括卧室、浴室和厨房。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>调查的进展和结果尚不清楚。特斯拉几年前就解散了公关部门，截至本文撰写时，马斯克尚未对该报道发表评论。然而，据报道，董事会想了解马斯克是否参与其中，以及工人的时间是否花在了这栋房子上。<em>彭博社</em>去年<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-07-21/tesla-tsla-executive-under-scrutiny-in-internal-probe">获悉</a>玻璃订单，但不了解董事会或 Project 42 的性质。</p><p>高管有时会获得像喷气式飞机这样的福利。不过，这些奖励的政策各不相同，特斯拉的做法相对严格。该汽车制造商要求董事会委员会对任何超过 120,000 美元的费用进行审计，并且相关人员（例如首席执行官）拥有重大利益。</p><p>这并不是一位知名科技高管第一次面临支出审查。 Meta <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sheryl-sandberg-meta-investigation-facebook-202644450.html">对即将离任的首席运营官谢丽尔·桑德伯格 (Sheryl Sandberg) 进行了调查</a>，指控她利用公司资源来实现个人目标，例如婚礼策划或试图压制批评她前合伙人鲍比·科蒂克 (Bobby Kotick) 的新闻报道。然而，马斯克作为主要首席执行官的形象使这个案例脱颖而出。</p><p>这位领导人对法律纠纷并不陌生。他仍然卷入<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-loses-appeal-to-tweet-whatever-he-wants-about-tesla-190942572.html">与美国证券交易委员会因推特财务数据而发生的争执</a>，并在英国洞穴探险家弗农·昂斯沃斯因未经证实的“恋童癖”指控而提起的诽谤诉讼中幸存下来。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/tesla-reportedly-suspected-musk-was-using-company-funds-to-build-a-literal-glass-house-193314854.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tesla-reportedly-suspected-musk-was-using-company-funds-to-build-a-literal-glass-house-193314854.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3a4ca2dc-7489-4202-b7e8-1216f0852d06</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 19:33:14 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689105662</ingested><modified> 2023-07-11T20:01:15+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="2427" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/90950c70-2025-11ee-af5d-75b79cd08cfa" width="3641"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2427" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/90950c70-2025-11ee-af5d-75b79cd08cfa" width="3641"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[LUDOVIC MARIN/POOL/AFP via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Electric car maker Tesla CEO Elon Musk looks on among other CEOs before a roundtable during the 6th edition of the "Choose France" Summit at the Chateau de Versailles, outside Paris on May 15, 2023. Since 2018, the Choose France S